1
00:00:00,125 --> 00:00:01,792
Maare aawabʼihom resil lix Hu laj Mormon,

2
00:00:01,792 --> 00:00:04,542
aʼbʼan maare taasachq aachʼool
rikʼin xnawbʼal kʼaʼru wan chi saʼ.

3
00:00:04,542 --> 00:00:05,334
Naʼilman chi najt,

4
00:00:05,334 --> 00:00:08,918
aʼan jun esil chirix jun nimla tenamit
li kitzʼiibʼaman chiru jun mil chihabʼ.

5
00:00:08,918 --> 00:00:09,834
Aʼbʼan saʼ xchʼoolil,

6
00:00:09,834 --> 00:00:12,083
aʼan naʼaatinak chirixebʼ
li kristiaan li keʼxyal

7
00:00:12,083 --> 00:00:14,542
xqʼe chixnawbʼal ru ut
chixtaaqenkil li Jesukristo.

8
00:00:14,542 --> 00:00:17,792
Natikla saʼ Jerusalen 600 chihabʼ ma
nayoʼla li Kristo naq kiyeheʼ re jun li

9
00:00:17,792 --> 00:00:21,209
profeet xbʼaan li Dios naq taaʼeeleliq
chiru li sachk tixkʼul li tenamit aʼan.

10
00:00:21,209 --> 00:00:23,459
Aʼan rochbʼeen lix junkabʼal
keʼkʼameʼ xbʼe chiru li

11
00:00:23,459 --> 00:00:26,000
palaw toj saʼ li chʼochʼ
nawbʼil ru joʼ America anajwan.

12
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,876
Keʼkʼihan li tenamit toj reetal naq
keʼxjachʼ ribʼ saʼ wiibʼ chi ninqi

13
00:00:28,876 --> 00:00:31,834
tenamit li wan naq keʼxpleeti ribʼ
ut wan naq keʼwan saʼ tuqtuukilal.

14
00:00:31,834 --> 00:00:34,667
Lix yuʼamebʼ aʼan naru nakateʼxmusiqʼa
chixpaabʼankil li Jesukristo,

15
00:00:34,667 --> 00:00:36,125
chi abʼink chiruhebʼ lix taqlahom,

16
00:00:36,125 --> 00:00:38,250
ut chi kʼanjelak chiruhebʼ
laa was aawiitzʼin.

17
00:00:38,250 --> 00:00:40,709
Wan saʼ lix Hu laj Mormon
li loqʼlaj aatin keʼxye li

18
00:00:40,709 --> 00:00:43,542
profeet li keʼxchʼolobʼ xyaalal
lix kʼulunik li Kolonel.

19
00:00:43,542 --> 00:00:46,209
Naxkʼut xyaalal li raatinul
li Santil Hu ut naxchʼolobʼ

20
00:00:46,209 --> 00:00:48,667
xyaalal naq li Jesukristo
aʼan li Ralal li Dios;

21
00:00:48,667 --> 00:00:49,792
naq kiwan xyuʼam, kikam,

22
00:00:49,792 --> 00:00:52,959
ut kinumta saʼ xbʼeen li kamk ut
li maak choqʼ re li junjunq qe.

23
00:00:52,959 --> 00:00:57,083
Xbʼaan aʼan naq kʼabʼaʼinbʼil “jun chik
chʼolobʼanbʼil esil chirix li Jesukristo.”​

24
00:00:57,083 --> 00:00:57,834
Relik chi yaal,

25
00:00:57,834 --> 00:01:01,792
li xnimal ru esilal saʼ li hu aʼan resil
lix kʼulunik li Jesukristo chiruhebʼ

26
00:01:01,792 --> 00:01:05,876
li tenamit saʼ li chʼochʼ America chirix
naq kiwakli chi yoʼyo aran Jerusalen.

27
00:01:05,876 --> 00:01:08,501
Aʼan naxkʼut lix evangelio,
naxkʼirtesihebʼ li yaj,

28
00:01:08,501 --> 00:01:10,125
ut narosobʼtesihebʼ li kokʼal.

29
00:01:10,125 --> 00:01:12,584
Aʼbʼan aʼan kaʼajwiʼ lix tiklajik li seraqʼ.

30
00:01:12,584 --> 00:01:16,209
Lix tzʼaqal tochʼom lix Hu laj
Mormon aʼan naq naru nakatxtenqʼa

31
00:01:16,209 --> 00:01:19,375
rikʼinebʼ li chʼaʼajkilal
nakanumsi saʼ li kutan aʼin.

32
00:01:19,375 --> 00:01:22,501
Naru nakataw xkʼojobʼankil aachʼool,
xbʼehil laa yuʼam,

33
00:01:22,501 --> 00:01:26,083
ut naru nakatzol chan ru
tatchaabʼiloʼq ut taasahoʼq aachʼool.

34
00:01:26,083 --> 00:01:27,292
Saʼ xbʼeen chixjunil,

35
00:01:27,292 --> 00:01:30,083
naru nakatnachʼo rikʼin
laa Kolonel Jesukristo.

